</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_231" id="115r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Johani Francken czu Bamberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Hersprucker, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie in Fricz Kracz und sein wirtin, des
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> stieftochter, mit
                                <expan>geistliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> czu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>umbtreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von sache und schulde wegen, darumb er in
                        doch vormals hie <expan>einproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey und sie genczlich
                        beczalt hab. Und darynne du vaste den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> F.
                        Kracz und <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> wirtin czu und dem
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ablegst, biten wir dich freuntlich und begern
                        von dir, daz du dich keiner <expan>unredlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache wider
                        den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> oder <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> unterwynden, sunder dir die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>freuntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen wöllest. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir gern ümb dich
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schulden</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>invocav<ex>i</ex><hi rend="sup">t</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
